  <summary date="2019-02-19T21:23:54Z" status="Introduced in House">Small Business Tax Equity Act of 2019

This bill exempts a trade or business that conducts marijuana sales in compliance with state law from a provision in the Internal Revenue Code that prohibits business-related tax credits or deductions for expenditures in connection with trafficking in controlled substances.</summary>
